quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  17,101,"wlqd atayna musaa tise mejzat wadhat shahdat ealaa sidq nbwth why: aleasa walyd walsnwn wanaqs althamarat waltwfan waljarad walqumal waldafadie waldm, fas'al -ayha alrswl- alyhwd sual taqrir hyn ja' musaa aslafhm bmejzath alwadhat, faqal fireawn lmwsa: 'iiniy la'azunuk -ya mwsa- sahra, mkhdweana mghlwbana ealaa eqlk bima tatyh min ghrayb alafeal"
  17,102,"frdd ealayh mwsa: laqad tyqqant -ya frewn- 'anah ma 'unzil tilk almejzat altise alshahdt ealaa sidq nbwty 'iilaa raba alsmwat walard; litakun dlalat yastdil biha 'uwlu albsayr ealaa whdanyt allah taealaa fi rbwbyth walwhyth, wa'iiniy lela yaqin 'anak -ya frewn- halik mlewn mghlwb"
  17,103,"farad fireawn 'ana yzej musaa wykhrjh mae bani 'iisrayiyl min 'ard \"msr\", fa'aghraqnah wman maeah min jnd fi albahr eqabana lhm"
  17,104,"wqlna min baed hlak fireawn wjndh libani 'israyyl: askunuu 'ard \"alsham\", fa'iidha ja' yawm alqiamat jina bikum jmyeana min qbwrkm 'iilaa mawqif alhsab"
  17,105,"wabialhaqi 'anzalna hdha alquran ealaa muhamad salaa allah ealayh wasalam lamr aleabbad wnhyhm wthwabhm weqabhm, wbalsdq waleadl walhfz min altaghyir waltbdyl nzl. wama 'arsalnak -ayha alrswl- 'iilaa mbshrana bialjanat liman atae, wmkhwfana bialnnar liman esa wkfr"
  17,106,"wanzlna 'iilayk -ayha alrswl- qranana byanah wahkmnah wfassalnah farqana bayn alhudaa waldalal walhaqa walbatl; litaqra'ah ealaa alnaas fi twdt wtmhhul, wnazzalnah mfrraqana, shyyana baed shy', ealaa hsb alhawadith wmqtdyat alahwal"
  17,107,"ql -ayha alrswl- lhwla' almkdhbyn: aminu bialquran 'aw la twmnu; fa'iina 'iimanikum la yzydh kmala wtkdhybkm la yulhiq bih nqsana. 'iina aleulama' aladhin 'uwtuu alkutub alssabiqat min qibal alqran, werfu hqyqt alwhy, 'iidha quri ealayhim alquran ykhshewn, fysjdwn ealaa wujuhuhum lilah subhanah wteala"
  17,108,"wyqwl hwla' aladhin 'uwtuu aleilm eind smae alqran: tnzyhana lrbna wtbryt lah mimaa ysfh almushrikun bh, ma kan waed allah taealaa min thawab weqab 'iilaa waqeana hqana"
  17,109,"wyqe hwla' sajidin ealaa wjwhhm, yabkun tathrana bmwaez alqran, wayaziduhum smae alquran wmwaezh khdweana li'amr allah wezym qdrth"
  17,110,"ql -ayha alrswl- lmshrky qawmak aladhin ankru ealayk alduea' bqwlk: ya allah ya rhmn, adeuu allh, 'aw adeuu alrhmn, fabi'ayi 'asmayih dewtmwh fa'iinakum tadeun rbana wahdana; li'ana asma'h klha hsna. wala tajhar balqra't fi slatk, fysmek almshrkwn, wala tusirr biha fala ysmek ashabk, wakun wstana bayn aljahr walhms"
  17,111,"wql -ayha alrswl-: alhamd lilah aladhi lah alkmal walthna', aldhy tnzzah ean alwld walsharik fi alwhyth, wala yakun lah subhanah wly min khalaqah fahu alghaniu alqwy, wahum alfuqara' almhtajwn 'ilyh, wezzimh tezymana tamana balthna' ealayh webadth wahdah la sharik lh, w'ikhlas aldiyn kuluh lh"